{"tid":2165730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：泛民五人拒絕警方破解手機兼取回手機申請被駁回兼輸訟費","createTime":"2020-08-20T04:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T05:23:56.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"18c9d9f4f86832226d6bea992799ecac3e10222b","tid":2165730,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"李柱銘等民主派人士被控組織及煽惑未經批准集結，警方早前取得法庭手令，欲破解和檢查李柱銘等五人的手機。五人向高等法院提出司法覆核，要求撤銷手令兼取回手機。案件早前審結，法官今頒下判詞，判五人敗訴，兼輸訟費。<br />\n<br />\n申請方質疑涉事手令授權警方的搜查範圍過闊，猶如讓警員搜屋時取走屋內所有物件，又指裁判官擔當把關角色，不宜聽到警方聲言進行搜查時不會違法，便相信他們並批出手令。警方則回應指，手令部份條款已能保障申請人，認為搜查不應受限。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/QGA5ODFJNZHTDHS3LVPT5PJQCI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FQGA5ODFJNZHTDHS3LVPT5PJQCI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=b50f93da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FQGA5ODFJNZHTDHS3LVPT5PJQCI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=bb22600a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/QGA5ODFJNZHTDHS3LVPT5PJQCI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"625d30a51a1dcbb0e914be767172105ebfe60199","tid":2165730,"uid":12463,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:20:13.000Z","msg":"好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f064640b25cfffd3044c51a7bdb484e464696b","tid":2165730,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:20:20.000Z","msg":"喺新疆講法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3516adac780e909c9e478ca8a1f1edd0d70a1ce","tid":2165730,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"反枱未"},{"pid":"380ecc4358c03dd70a17705c71e539a872b4152c","tid":2165730,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f667ad72ad53d3b63a0931e446a740fa7bd80b","tid":2165730,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:44:42.000Z","msg":"判詞全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=130295&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D130295%26currpage%3DT&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=9ac1bf83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=130295&amp;currpage=T</a>"},{"pid":"13d6e398a3be3e66038fd17178f717b17dacd1a6","tid":2165730,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:51:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"735c8ea6f8990949c9c70e8f1a81220f2a6006da","tid":2165730,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:21:41.000Z","msg":"oush"},{"pid":"ba1f8ed1fe33a5008229c9ce51a312cfb84d393e","tid":2165730,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李柱銘等民主派人士被控組織及煽惑未經批准集結，警方早前取得法庭手令，欲破解和檢查李柱銘等五人的手機。五人向高等法院提出司法覆核，要求撤銷手令兼取回手機。案件早前審結，法官今頒下判詞，判五人敗訴，兼輸訟費。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李柱銘可以講法治已死未？"},{"pid":"fafccba337fff529a8d2c42e67de86ddaaef02dd","tid":2165730,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,